definitions.definition: ( chiefly in the plural ) Alternative spelling of pastie ( “ a small item of clothing that conceals little more than the nipple of a woman 's breast , primarily worn by female exotic dancers ” ) .

main_definition: A type of seasoned meat and vegetable hand pie , usually of a semicircular shape.
